snippet.title: The Frogs Official Trailer - Steam Cut
snippet.description:
This is a trailer for The Frogs, a point-and-click adventure game based on the play by Aristophanes. All of the art is done with animated Renaissance paintings backed up with public domain classical music.

Wishlist and play the Demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1589610/The_Frogs/
Play the Free Demo NOW! https://gamejolt.com/games/thefrogs/595985
Check out my webpage at https://www.mijawells.com/.
Keep an eye out for it on Kickstarter!
